channel.title: Pb's Cheat Client
channel.description:
This is my cheat client with most of the things working. It has: [code] Cheats: NoClip- Undetectable noclip command.. simply makes it so you can walk through shit..(undetectable unless someone sees you) Client Drop-Undetectable client drop(instantly logs you out) unless someones sees you... they'll think it's x-logging Attempt Crash- Trys to crash the server(sends packet 139 with a value of -1) won't work on most dodian servers Spawn Item(Credits to bomb)- Prompts you to type in an item you wish to spawn(appears in your second inventory slot) Bank- 'clicks' a bankbooth..(sends packet 252 and clicks object 2213) Works on most Delta servers(a few exceptions) Object Click- Prompts you to enter in an object to click(packet 132) Object Click2- Prompts you to enter in an object to click option 2(packet 252) Auto-Alch(credits to AZN)- Auto alches last item you alched manually(must first alch an item manually) Login Mask- Stupid attempt to change your name clientside.. didn't feel like following through with it(NOT WORKING) Object Click Loop- Loops clicking an object until you turn it off Object Click2 Loop- Loops clicking an object option 2 until you turn it off Buy 10 Loop- Enter in Item ID and Slot(First slot = 0) (seperated by space) with a Shop interface open to Keep buying 10 of that Item(Enter: "882 1" to loop
buy rune arrows in the second slot) Sell 10 Loop- Same as above just your selling from your inventory (Enter: "882 0" to sell rune arrows in your first inventory slot, Works anywhere!)
Bot: *Note: All bots are timed according to default delta values.. so if its off blame the server creator.. feel free to try to edit them* Mine Ess- Mines essence anywhere and banks the ess after a full inventory(Usually requires a pickaxe to be wielded, Depends on Server) Mine Addy- Mines addy.. after like 6 it banks.. not timed right(works anywhere) Woodcutting- Enter in a tree to cut(Enter: "yew") and it'll cut Yew trees *Read Woodcutting list for proper Trees to enter*(works anywhere) RuneCrafting- (Ess must be in first bank Slot)Enter in a rune to make(Enter: "nat") and it'll make nature runes*Read RuneCrafting list for proper Runes to
enter*(works anywhere) FireMake- (Logs must be in first bank Slot) Enter in a log to burn(Enter: "yew) and it'll burn yew logs*Read the Woodcutting list for proper Logs to enter*
(works anywhere) Fletch Shortbow-(Logs must be in first bank Slot & Requires a knife in first inventory slot) Enter in a log to cut(Enter: Yew) and it'll make yew
shortbows*Read the Woodcutting list for proper Logs to enter*(works anywhere) Fletch Longbow-Same as above... just cuts Longbows instead Auto Reconnect- If you disconnect from the server it'll try to reconnect with the same username and password and if it fails.. it'll try again in 15 seconds
Debug: Debug Items- Shows Item id when you right click an item Deubg Npcs- Shows Npc id when you right click an npc Debug Objects- Shows an Object id when you right click an object Fps Toggle- Toggles Frames per Second display on and off Script Timer- Shows Script Timer in seconds in the console Mouse Packet- Shows information in the console everytime a mouse packet is sent(whether it be real or fake)
Commands(enter in the chatbox): "--noclip"= Noclips "--rights x" = (Credits to Bomb)Enter in 0-2 in place of x to change your clientside playerrights(basically just so you can see a crown) "--admin" = (Credits to Bomb)Makes you have a gold crown next to your name(changes rights to 2) "--mod" = (Credits to Bomb)Makes you have a silver crown next to your name(changes rights to 1) "--norm" = (Credits to Bomb)Makes you have no crown next to your name(changes rights to 0) "--closeinterface" = Closes any open interface... clientside of course. "--openinterface" = (Credits to Bomb) Opens the interface you enter after it(5292 = bank) Won't do anything substantial as it doesn't set the inventory
overlay "--dropclient" = Instantly logs you out... "--openbank" = Opens bank with proper overlay... won't work because the server has a failsafe against this "--bank" = Banks Item entered after with the slot entered after that(requires bank to be open)(Enter: "--bank 1042 0" to bank a blue partyhat in your first
inventory slot) "--sell" = Sells 1 of the Item in your inventory at the specified slot(first slot = 0)(Enter: "--sell 1042 0" to sell a blue partyhat in your first inventory
slot) "--buy" = Same as above.. just buys and the slot is relative to the store you're buying from "--gitem" = (Credits to Bomb) Spawns a ground item like 8 spaces away cuz the ground items are fucked up.. never got to fixing... usually picking up doesnt
work(server checks if its there)(Enter: "--gitem 1042 1") "--sobject" = (Credits to Bomb) Spawns an object at your location.. only you can see it(as this is clientside)(Enter: "--sobject 2213") "--invis" = Makes you invisible to everybody(works on all servers) "--finvis" = Makes you reappear with my favorite look ;) "--useitem" = Enter in the two slots of the items you wish to use on each other (Enter: "--useitem 0 27" to use the first item in your inventory with the
last) "--coords" = Sends you your coordinates in the chatbox [/code] Client Download: http://uppit.com/zdwfai0ryo6l/Jon's_Cheat_Client.rar Credits: Me Bombs AZN Moparscape for tuts
